title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 §§ 1-1.9 - Reports

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 §§ 1-1.9 - Reports

State Regulations

Tax Law, section 211(1)

The term "report" means a report or return of tax but
does not include an estimated tax filing. Notes
